{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was kind of fortunate because about six, seven months down the line, the accountant took a liking to me and he used to invite me over to dinner at his house.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and one day he says to me, you know, I got an extra spare room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My wife and my son would love to have you staying at-- at my house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So prior to that, one day I'm in-- we had dormitories where we slept and then we had a little room there with, like, 10 guys.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had lockers and we had a table around with-- with benches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's where we hang around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a PA system.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I get a PA message, Harold Blitzer, you have a visitor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So now I go downstairs and it's-- it's a Israel soldier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He has a-- has a British uniform but he's got Palestine written up here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I didn't spoke Hebrew, I could hardly speak any English at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we got sort of along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He tells me, here's a letter from your father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was packages of 400 cigarettes, Palestinian cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because the reason cigarettes was that was the currency after the war in Europe, cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was based on cigarettes, which is amazing but they didn't know about cancer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But those years, bread than Germany-- it was-- it was all based on cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So even in our camp, we had the-- the currency was dollars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was figured out that a bread was so much and a-- and a-- it was either in dollars or cigarettes, although we weren't allowed to smoke and we weren't allowed to-- and probably nobody had any dollars.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
